Packages 
Package Description
org.jdom2.jaxb
This package contains experimental classes from the JDOM development branch that are utilized by XFlat.
org.xflatdb.xflat
This package contains the public interface for XFlat.
org.xflatdb.xflat.convert
This package contains the conversion interface exposed by XFlat.
org.xflatdb.xflat.convert.converters
This package contains basic converters implemented for common conversion types.
org.xflatdb.xflat.db
This package contains the core classes for XFlat.
org.xflatdb.xflat.engine
This package contains the implementations of Engine that are provided by XFlat out of the box.
org.xflatdb.xflat.query
This package contains classes related to XPath-based queries.
org.xflatdb.xflat.transaction
This package contains all the classes related to the public transaction API, as well as the main TransactionManager implementations.
org.xflatdb.xflat.util
This package contains various utilities in use by the core XFlat classes.
